{"tid":127941,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"學生自殺可以係樣子問題","createTime":"2017-02-20T12:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T14:29:17.000Z","uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb767e1b78d0b2f9049fc366590c69294cf32a68","tid":127941,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"父母諗下 你比左個咩外貌自己個仔女（係依個外貌行先既年代）<br />\n<br />\n第二 文化  你地個文化係中國 所以叫自己中國人 <br />\n<br />\n但係你地自己本身都歧視大陸人<br />\n我做你個仔聽得你講大陸仔啲野多<br />\n都知大陸係負面既形容詞<br />\n仲點會想認做中國人<br />\n<br />\n第三 <br />\n比你察覺到唔正常咁一定係佢已經壓力好大，<br />\n通常都係比人灌輸忍左去既概念。<br />\n或者根本你都唔會理佢<br />\n一句<br />\n係咁架啦 就當無事<br />\n<br />\n自殺 內向既多數都唔想令你地擔心，所以會扮正常。 到佢地死左 你地仲話察覺唔到 真係太遲。<br />\n<br />\n第四 朋輩影響 同垃圾老師<br />\n<br />\n老師只會幫識擦鞋 樣靚既學生<br />\n<br />\n根本唔一定關讀書事<br />\n<br />\n諗到再補充<br />\n<br />\n：過來人"},{"pid":"5fc75b717eda0e6951848798194421de7129db7d","tid":127941,"uid":75095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:18:54.000Z","msg":"過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41abe27079efab28620a9f60bd2d6fc937c21bf","tid":127941,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:32:31.000Z","msg":"如果上帝真係公平<br />\n點解唔所有野都一樣<br />\n<br />\n比條爛命我<br />\n<br />\nOn99"},{"pid":"0cd12d5e3d0c2ffe8e4b8478201c77709aaeaab5","tid":127941,"uid":22888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果上帝真係公平<br />\n點解唔所有野都一樣<br />\n<br />\n比條爛命我<br />\n<br />\nOn99</blockquote><br />\n係上帝比你既考驗啊"},{"pid":"4934f638a02cf4db8d24c84a30a877ec9d04c10a","tid":127941,"uid":53698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:35:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果上帝真係公平<br />\n點解唔所有野都一樣<br />\n<br />\n比條爛命我<br />\n<br />\nOn99</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個世界究竟有冇神 <br />\n如果真係有 點解要有咁多人要受苦難<br />\n生靈塗炭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a388e3f0cb9de81ae76165155f3d6009fa4ff9a","tid":127941,"uid":5497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:38:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果上帝真係公平<br />\n點解唔所有野都一樣<br />\n<br />\n比條爛命我<br />\n<br />\nOn99</blockquote><br />\n肯定有人同你講，上帝係公平既，就算靚仔有錢佢都會有野差過你，你要做既係感恩同奉獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f0c1939ba47d7211d733a003c49d0dea56db31","tid":127941,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:32:42.000Z","msg":"因為上帝並唔係公平"},{"pid":"f81bb4d4593f3f72f901e09082b8e94b9546c6bb","tid":127941,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:16:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果上帝真係公平<br />\n點解唔所有野都一樣<br />\n<br />\n比條爛命我<br />\n<br />\nOn99</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個世界究竟有冇神 <br />\n如果真係有 點解要有咁多人要受苦難<br />\n生靈塗炭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依d係所謂神既考驗啊<br />\n你唔信就會落地獄架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8247833aefb005b94334fed08217e204fa229bd6","tid":127941,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:29:17.000Z","msg":"世界係唔公平"}]}